'''栗耳阿拉卡鴷'''（''Pteroglossus castanotis''）是[[南美洲|南美洲]]中部及東南部特有的一種[[巨嘴鳥|巨嘴鳥]]。牠們像[[黑頸阿拉卡鴷|黑頸阿拉卡鴷]]，但體型較大及色彩鮮艷。

==分佈==
栗耳阿拉卡鴷分佈在[[亞馬遜盆地|亞馬遜盆地]]，尤其集中於西南部。牠們也分佈於[[安地斯山脈|安地斯山脈]]東部，直達[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]中南部。

亞馬遜盆地南部分佈地向[[亞瑪遜河|亞瑪遜河]]上游延伸，東南向[[喜拉朵|喜拉朵]]中部及南部，集結於東[[巴拉圭|巴拉圭]]的[[巴拉那河|巴拉那河]]、[[巴西|巴西]]東南部及[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]的極北端。<ref name=Bencke2007>Bencke, Glayson Ariel (2007): Avifauna atual do Rio Grande do Sul, Brasil: aspectos biogeográficos e distribucionais ["The Recent avifauna of Rio Grande do Sul: Biogeographical and distributional aspects"]. Talk held on 2007-JUN-22 at ''Quaternário do RS: integrando conhecimento'', Canoas, Rio Grande do Sul, Brazil. [http://www6.ufrgs.br/alpp/Resumos_Quaternario_RS.pdf PDF abstract] {{Wayback|url=http://www6.ufrgs.br/alpp/Resumos_Quaternario_RS.pdf |date=20170708084133 }}</ref>.

==寄生蟲==
栗耳阿拉卡鴷上[[寄生|寄生]]了一種稱為''Austrophilopterus flavirostris''的[[蝨|蝨]]。<ref name=PriceWeckstein2005>{{Cite journal en|author=Price, Roger D. & Weckstein, Jason D.|year=2005|title=The genus ''Austrophilopterus'' Ewing (Phthiraptera: Philopteridae) from toucans, toucanets, and araçaris (Piciformes: Ramphastidae)|journal=Zootaxa|volume=918|pages=1-18|url=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2005f/z00918f.pdf|access-date=2009-05-13|archive-date=2019-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723233531/https://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2005f/z00918f.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

